  "instructions": [
    "Wash and dry the romaine lettuce, then shred it into bite‑size pieces and place in a large bowl.",
    "Add the diced cucumber, halved cherry tomatoes, and sliced red onion to the lettuce.",
    "Pour in the rinsed chickpeas, crumbled feta, and sliced olives.",
    "In a small bowl whisk together the olive oil, lemon juice, minced garlic, red pepper flakes, black pepper, and sea salt until the dressing is emulsified.",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss gently so all ingredients are evenly coated.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning with extra salt or pepper if needed.",
    "Serve immediately on a chilled plate or bowl for a refreshing, fluffy salad.",
    "Optional: garnish with a sprinkle of chopped parsley or a drizzle of extra olive oil for extra aroma."
